納","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-814e-9ceb-c7d8546e0b2d","type":"numbered_list_item","parent":"2. `num`を一つ増やす","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8164-a1f9-e9c2a304a15c","type":"numbered_list_item","parent":"3. `num`を文字列型に変換して、`ft.Text`コントロールの`value`に格納","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8178-a19f-e755d102f00b","type":"numbered_list_item","parent":"4. `ft.Text`コントロールを`update`する","children":[]}]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-810a-970b-c300d2a6b6e0","type":"paragraph","parent":"※ファイルは「flet-prac3.py」として保存","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-817a-b6be-db8d787202d9","type":"heading_1","parent":"# 進捗アンケート","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81b1-a9c0-fb0d977b154c","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8190-a55a-f0a7bbc331ee","type":"paragraph","parent":"この問題が終了した人は、以下のGoogleフォームに回答してください。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81b2-9321-efe5aba59462","type":"paragraph","parent":"回答後、練習問題の回答例のURLをメールでお送りします。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-810c-8214-dc56bd3da6aa","type":"quote","parent":"> ","children":[{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81fa-888c-e171e62e8a77","type":"bookmark","parent":"[bookmark](https://forms.gle/FFBeAXNS5VA5AJV29)","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81e1-b283-f4c0913716e1","type":"paragraph","parent":"","children":[]}]}],"pageNavs":[{"title":"Home","id":"/posts"},{"title":"基礎班カリキュラム","id":"/posts/course/basic"},{"title":"前期","id":"/posts/course/前期"},{"title":"Flet","id":"/posts/curriculums/1ada501e-f337-81b0-9f36-fca0cbc695ea/1ada501e-f337-81b0-9f36-fca0cbc695ea"},{"id":"/posts/curriculums/1ada501e-f337-81b0-9f36-fca0cbc695ea/1ada501e-f337-817c-8161-e5789a7e37f4","title":"Fletの練習問題3"}],"childrenData":{"title":"Flet","childPages":[{"title":"0. GUIとFletについて","id":"1ada501e-f337-813a-8c94-db33d2a2aba8"},{"title":"1. Fletのインストール","id":"1ada501e-f337-8127-a1ab-e7c4e69a6f4a"},{"title":"2. カウンターを作ってみよう","id":"1ada501e-f337-8189-8b63-dbb7026b58e2"},{"title":"3. ページの生成","id":"1ada501